<sect1>Compilation and Installation
<p>
Compiling Pab is very easy. The following should do it:
<code>
&percnt; ./configure
&percnt; make
&percnt; make install
</code>

That should do it! Should you run into any problems, please report them
 to the <htmlurl url="mailto:dsanders@kde.org" name="author">

